Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.48,0:24:39.94,On Screen red,,0,0,0,,[In it were the summer memories of an encounter\Nwith Madao, and then their farewell...]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.94,0:24:45.11,On Screen red,,0,0,0,,[See you next time.]
